OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FExceptionally
OL,6,Fwarm into the evening and overnight,
OL,7,Fwith late sunshine for many. However,
OL,8,Fsome far western areas may see
OL,9,Fsporadic showery rain and some
OL,10,Fthundery outbreaks spread erratically
OL,11,Fnortheast, with locally strong, gusty
OL,12,Fwinds, hail and isolated downpours
OL,13,Fpossible here.
OL,14,
OL,15,CFriday:FExceptionally hot, markedly
OL,16,Fhotter than Thursday for many areas,
OL,17,Fin another mainly fine day with
OL,18,Fsunshine, this sunshine perhaps
OL,19,Fperiodically hazy. Gusty, thundery
OL,20,Fdownpours possible initially, mainly
OL,21,Fin west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
