OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FThe
OL,6,Fhot spell gradually coming to an end:
OL,7,Fstill very warm on Saturday but with
OL,8,Fincreasing potential for thundery
OL,9,Foutbreaks, progressively introducing
OL,10,Ffresher conditions by the end of the
OL,11,Fweekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
